The classic dm_overwatch for css.

place for 30 players, working radar (i hope),buyzones, no bomb no hostages- 
i recommend to play this map with a deathmatch or gungame mod


there are still some little reflection errors but i cant get them fixed. i dont know if its even possible to fix these since valve messed up the cubemaps.

but it should be good enough to have fun on it.

if wished i can try to port more hl2/hl2dm maps to css.

enjoy~
